                                    <li>(i) “<strong>Data Controller</strong>” has the meaning set out in GDPR;</li>
                                    <li>(ii) “<strong>Data Processor</strong>” has the meaning set out in GDPR;</li>
                                    <li>(iii) “<strong>Data Protection Regulator</strong>” means the applicable
                                        supervisory authority with jurisdiction over either party, and in each case any
