                                        Personal Information including but not limited to Regulation (EU) 2016/679 (the
                                        “<strong>General Data Protection Regulation</strong>” or
                                        “<strong>GDPR</strong>”); and</li>
                                    <li>(vi) “<strong>Process</strong>”, “<strong>Processing</strong>” or
